article.headline: Texas State University 86, TCU 44
article.story:
FORT WORTH, Texas (AP)-- Ashley Davis scored 14 points and
Sandora Irvin added 13 points and 10 rebounds in TCU's 86-44
victory over Texas State on Friday night.

Irvin grabbed six offensive rebounds and blocked five shots for
the Lady Frogs, who were 9-of-18 from 3-point range and
outrebounded Texas State 50-31.

Ally Kelly scored 10 points for Texas State (0-1), which shot 28
percent from the field and went 8-of-20 from the line. The Bobcats
also had 27 turnovers, which the Lady Frogs turned into 33 points.
